dct_description_sm: No relief shown. Some buildings represented pictorially List and location of tourist sights, including Public Squares, Railway Stations, State Services, Public Buildings and Monuments, Clubs and Sports Grounds, Museums, Archeological Sites, Byzantine Churches, and Churches of Various Denominations. Shows post offices and telegrams/telephones. Verso: inset map of Greece and surrounding area (no scale) and a list of guided tours and cruises.
